# Environment Variables

Add these to your `.env.local` file (create it in the root directory):

## Supabase Configuration

```env
# Supabase API Configuration
# Get these values from: https://app.supabase.com -> Settings -> API
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-id.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here
```

## Important Notes

- ⚠️ Never commit `.env.local` to version control (it's already in `.gitignore`)
- The `VITE_` prefix makes variables available in your frontend code
- Never put your service role key in frontend environment variables
- Restart your dev server after changes to `.env.local`
